high_descs: Turn around, go forward, then turn right to go to the cabinet adjacent to the stove.
Pick up the plate from the cabinet, adjacent to the stove.
Turn left, move forward, then look up to face the microwave.
Warm up the plate in the microwave.
Go to the sink to your right.
Put the plate in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward, then hang a right and walk up to the counter.
Open the lower cabinet to the right of the oven and take out of the grey plate, then close the cabinet door.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the oven and look up at the microwave.
Put the plate in the microwave and turn on the microwave, after a couple seconds take out the plate and close the microwave.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the heated plate in the sink basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated plate in the sink.

high_descs: Open the left cabinet door and grab the plate.
Head over to the microwave and open the door.
Heat the plate in the microwave and take it out.
Place the plate in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the plate in the sink.
